contestNewFormByContests: In case of a tie, it will be broken by time. Time will be measured between the moment that the contest started and the moment each problem was solved.

demotionProblemEmailBannedBody:
Dear %(user_name):

The access to your problem %(problem_name) in omegaUp has been restricted because it was reported as inappropriate. The omegaUp team has reviewed this report and confirmed that the problem is not appropriate because %(reason).

To unblock the problem and have it appear again in the list of problems, please follow the steps below:

  1. Review and edit your problem: make sure you describe a problem, it is not offensive or spam.
  2. Once you have resolved the reason on why your problem was blocked, send an email quality@omegaup.com to be reviewed and reactivated.

If the steps mentioned above are not followed, the problem will not be shown again in the list of problems, nor can it be used in competitions. In case of a relapse in three occasions, omegaUp reserves the right to suspend your user account.

omegaUp is a platform to help users improve their software engineering skills by solving code problems and competing in programing contests. omegaUp welcomes all the problems that help meet that goal.

Thanks,

omegaUp team

To remove the warning notification on the problem please follow the steps below:

  1. Review and edit your problem.
  2. Once you have resolved the reason on why a warning has been put on your problem, send an email to quality@omegaup.com to be reviewed.

    3. If the steps mentioned above are not followed, the problem will show a warning sign in the list of problems.
